{"tid":1658571,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"岑子杰遇襲 如何反擊","createTime":"2019-10-16T14:00:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T05:38:10.000Z","uid":266780,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cd0e33107a1d7b79fee3bfd58a0f6fc4e1597480","tid":1658571,"uid":266780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:00:09.000Z","msg":"梁天琦獄中語港人：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">勿被仇恨支配<br />\n保持警覺思考</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n美國戰線，已行到一半，就到手<br />\n我地仲有LBJ助攻<br />\n<br />\n其他國家的戰線，都開始了<br />\n<br />\n無錯，戰事有排未完<br />\n但，認清目標<br />\n我地要中共在全世界都無運行<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林奠，黑狗，我們要反擊<br />\n我們要他們百倍奉還<br />\n<br />\n但我們不可被怒火仇恨支配<br />\n我們不是他們<br />\n我們是香港人<br />\n真正的香港人<br />\n<br />\n若我們無差別地放火，裝修，鶳<br />\n咁我地同何妖無分別<br />\n火魔法，可以用<br />\n裝修，可以做<br />\n鶳，可以召喚<br />\n<br />\n但<br />\n<br />\n不要無差別<br />\n<br />\n要有目標<br />\n有理有據<br />\n有策略<br />\n<br />\n記住，不要火遮眼<br />\n一子錯，我地就會輸<br />\n<br />\n無你地，行唔到今日<br />\n勇武，你永遠是我們最好的戰士<br />\n<br />\n一和理非"},{"pid":"a7d02e071bda987185e37c8540cd3749ef41845e","tid":1658571,"uid":209543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:01:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a669ef37e413a090b7707f157cf6798c105e855e","tid":1658571,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:02:22.000Z","msg":"屌你老母岑子杰單野我要響國際新聞見到！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1658212\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1658212</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n全世界同我落<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#PrayForJimmy</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-la